Comments are something to add to make the code easier to read, and to make others mabye understand it better, or just to simply add notes. 
Comments are also "invinseble" and is ignored by the compiler.

Single line comment look like this: //This is a comment. 

A Multi-line comments look like this:

/* This is a single-line comment */
        /*  This is an example of
            a multi-line comment */
----------------------------------------
